<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Setup Section</title>
  
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }
        header {
            background: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .section h3 {
            color: #0056b3;
        }
        .section p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .section a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 10px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .section a:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <h1>Setup guide</h1>
</header>
<div class="container">
    <h2>Setup Your Account</h2>

    <div class="section">
        <h3>For New Users</h3>
        <p>If you are new to our platform, please sign up to create your account. Once registered, you can start searching for properties or listing your own.</p>
        <a href="/signup">Sign Up</a>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h3>For Existing Users</h3>
        <p>If you already have an account, please log in to access your dashboard, manage your bookings, or view your property listings.</p>
        <a href="/login">Log In</a>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h3>For Property Owners</h3>
        <p>If you are a property owner and wish to list your property on our platform, sign up or log in to your account, then head to the "List Your Property" section in your dashboard.</p>
        <a href="/listings/new">List Your Property</a>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; 2024 Ghar.com  All rights reserved.</p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
